Error: Problem: "Internal Exception: Io.Netty.Handler.Codec.EncoderException: Java.Lang.NullPointerException" Error Occurs When Attempting To Join A Minecraft Server.

Solution: 1. First, make sure that you have the latest version of Java installed on your computer.
2. Verify that your internet connection is stable and strong enough to connect to the server.
3. Check if the server is updated to the latest version of Minecraft.
4. Try connecting to a different Minecraft server to see if the error persists.
